Scroller - Class in <Unnamed>
CLASS: Scroller (extends Object) AUTHOR: danpost (greenfoot.org username) DATE: November 11, 2016 MODIFIED: December 22, 2016 (fixed 'scroll' method for limited no-image scrolling) MODIFIED: February 21, 2017 (fixed scroll offsets for unlimited no-image scrolling) DESCRIPTION: This is a support class for a scrolling world.
Scroller(World, GreenfootImage) - Constructor for class Scroller
This constructor is for an unlimited scrolling world; If 'image' is null, the background will not change; else the given image is wrapped
Scroller(World, GreenfootImage, int, int) - Constructor for class Scroller
This constructor is for a limited scrolling world; If 'image' is smaller than the given total scrolling area, it will be tiled If 'image' is null, the background will not change
